## Inputs and Outputs

| Input | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| Hardware | GLFW Events | Detected via `glfw.joystick_present()`, `glfw.get_joystick_axes()`, and `glfw.get_joystick_buttons()`. |

| Output | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| Parameter Updates | Float / Int | Triggers parameter changes in VJLive3's `Matrix` based on bound axes/buttons. |

